name: 【 Self_Love 】
description:
All you need is (self) love.

Made with both hands at the same time.
 
Right hand was red.
Left one was blue.


Part of an experiment I'm doing about drawing with both hands at the same time in a furious rush of emotion and feelings. That time I needed some company, or a hug but the only thing I had in that moment was my own hands and art. 

Crayons an both hands
3516x2615
